    "slug": "dastardly-planner",
    "description": "<p>During Combat, the user maintains a Dastard Clock, which is 8 Spans in size.<br><br>Whenever the user uses the Wait Action, or an action with the @Trait[set-up] trait (not inclusive of Resolution phase), Tick Forward the Dastard Clock by one Span.When the user declares an Attack, the Dastard Clock Empties. <br><br>For each Span removed in this way, if the Attack is a Damaging Attack, increase its Power by 10%. Additionally, for each 2 Spans removed, add +1 to the duration of any non-[Weather], [Terrain], or [Room] effects the triggering Attack creates or inflicts.</p>",
